
1. References
 - Official site 
  + https://mmonit.com/monit/
 - Document
  + https://mmonit.com/monit/documentation/monit.html
  
2. Configuration
 - monitrc
  + default location
   * ~/.monitrc or /etc/monitrc
 - monit daemon
  + ip/port : 127.0.0.1:2812 by default
  + account : admin/monit by default
  
3. Command-line commands
 - check version
  + monit -V
 - check control file for syntax errors
  + monit -t
 - Start/Stop monit process 
  + start 
   * monit 
   * monit -c /var/monit/monitrc 
  + stop
   * monit quit
  
4. managing services
 - e.g. monit -g www stop
  
4. Add-ons
 - pingdom (https://www.pingdom.com/)
